.DT
add_command
Disk World creator help
add_command

.SH Name
.SP 5 5
add_command -  A simul_efun for add_command.
.EP

.SH Syntax
.SI 5
varargs void add_command(string verb,
string pattern,
function func)
.EI

.SH Parameters
.SI 5
%^BOLD%^verb%^RESET%^ - the verb to add
%^BOLD%^pattern%^RESET%^ - the pattern associated with the verb
%^BOLD%^func%^RESET%^ - the funvction to call on success

.EI

.SH Defined in
.SI 5
/secure/simul_efun/add_command.c
.EI

.SH Description
.SP 5 5

A simul_efun for add_command.  This allows you to call add_command without
having to go this_player()->add_command.  This will only work on non-living
objects.

.EP

.SH See also
.SP 5 5
/global/new_parse->add_command(), help add_command_conversion

.EP

